Download an Ubuntu ISO-image from 
http://www.ubuntu.com/download

Download VirtualBox from
http://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

Install VirtualBox using the easy step-by-step installer

Start VirtualBox by double-clicking on its icon or whatever you do on your OS to start an installed application.
Click on the "New" blue sun-looking icon in the VirtualBox GUI to create a new VM

sudo apt-get install default-jdk

